<headline>Severe Thunderstorm Watch issued March 06 at 2:37AM EST until March 06 at 5:00AM EST by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>THE NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE HAS EXTENDED SEVERE THUNDERSTORM
WATCH 31 TO INCLUDE THE FOLLOWING AREAS UNTIL 5 AM EST EARLY THIS
MORNING
IN INDIANA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 7 COUNTIES
IN NORTHERN INDIANA
ADAMS                 ALLEN IN              BLACKFORD
HUNTINGTON            JAY                   WELLS
WHITLEY
THIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF BERNE, BLUFFTON, COLUMBIA CITY,
DECATUR, DUNKIRK, FORT WAYNE, HARTFORD CITY, HUNTINGTON,
MONTPELIER, NEW HAVEN, OSSIAN, PORTLAND, ROANOKE, SOUTH WHITLEY,
AND TRI-LAKES.</description>
